Chain Combo.forced_motion: function (agi, dex, hits) { return 1 - (0.004 * agi) - (0.002 * dex); });

Combo Finish.forced_motion: function (agi, dex, hits) { return 0.7 - (0.004 * agi) - (0.002 * dex); });
